                <span class="comment-copy" style="border-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(36, 39, 41); column-rule-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); display: inline;">Actually, timeit tests show ndarray operations such as <code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(36, 39, 41); column-rule-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); display: inline;">np.dot(array2, array2)</code> are faster than <code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(36, 39, 41); column-rule-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); display: inline;">matrix1*matrix2</code>. This makes sense because <code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(36, 39, 41); column-rule-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); display: inline;">matrix</code> is a subclass of ndarray which overrides special methods like <code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(36, 39, 41); column-rule-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); display: inline;">__mul__</code>. <a href="https://github.com/numpy/numpy/blob/master/numpy/matrixlib/defmatrix.py#L306" rel="nofollow noreferrer" style="border-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 119, 204); cursor: pointer; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-decoration: underline solid rgb(0, 119, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: underline; -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); display: inline;"><code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 119, 204); cursor: pointer; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(0, 119, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: underline; -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); display: inline;">matrix.__mul__</code> calls <code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 119, 204); cursor: pointer; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(0, 119, 204); column-rule-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: underline; -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(0, 119, 204); display: inline;">np.dot</code></a>. So there is code reusage here. Instead of performing fewer checks, using <code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(36, 39, 41); column-rule-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); display: inline;">matrix*matrix</code> requires an extra function call. So the advantage of using <code style="background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); border-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: auto; line-height: 16.9px; list-style-type: none; outline-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none solid rgb(36, 39, 41); column-rule-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); backdrop-filter: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); -webkit-text-emphasis-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); color-interpolation: srgb; color-interpolation-filters: linearrgb; paint-order: normal; caret-color: rgb(36, 39, 41); display: inline;">matrix</code> is purely syntactic, not better performance.</span>
                
